This directory contains examples of programs
that are too big to put into a textbook.

On page 146 of CBD 4/e we wrote that we would
provide more examples of multifile programs.
Here are some examples:

   c_align     -- align comments on the right
   lu_decomp   -- find the LU-decomposition of a matrix
   mk_cols     -- make columns using the words in a file
   palindrome  -- versions of the palindrome program
   wrt_char    -- write character information on the screen
